subject: New file that mentions SEVEN
author: Kristin
full_text:
I am going through my session that I did yesterday and I asked for
their names.  For some reason I can never get a name or I get tons of
them.  Yesterday was no different.  When I asked again they said:

CALL US.... WE'RE ... I AM.. SEVEN

Not sure that means anything - but interesting none the less :-)
It's in my file (Kristin's File).
